<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Pratfall is a game where you fall, dig, explode and rescue your dog! Navigate deadly caves solo or with friends in this chaotic co-op adventure. Team up with friends and watch your step on this journey full of traps, hazards, and the most deadly force of all: gravity. Will you jump into the unknown to rescue your dog?
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="324" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4244510/extras/7935d2a0730df1effd71e5e40e677b52.poster.avif?t=1776707033" width="960">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4244510/extras/7935d2a0730df1effd71e5e40e677b52.webm?t=1776707033" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
