   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   RESCUE YOUR DOG
  </strong>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Wait, why is there even a construction site in this dog park? Your best friend fell down a hole and needs your help! Grab a helmet, a pickaxe, and some friends to head after your buddy.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="324" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4244510/extras/c221a1ce919a0bf2b8d09f079636f7be.poster.avif?t=1776707033" width="960">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4244510/extras/c221a1ce919a0bf2b8d09f079636f7be.webm?t=1776707033" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4244510/extras/c221a1ce919a0bf2b8d09f079636f7be.mp4?t=1776707033" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   DON'T FALL (TOO MUCH)
  </strong>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  There’s a huge system of caves down there, and this rescue mission might be tougher than expected! Luckily,
  <i>
   someone
  </i>
  ordered a bunch of items that are scattered and buried all over the place. Find food to recover from injuries, use ziplines to cross crevasses, or create your own path with your pickaxe, drill, and magic beans. Don't forget to light the way with flares, it's dark down there!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
